---
title: Cherry-Glazed Pork & Garlic Mash with Lemony Veggies & Parmesan Cheese
description: The glaze on these pork steaks is everything you want and more - sweet, sticky, fruity and acidic all at once. That’s why we’ve kept the sides simple on this one. What else could you possibly need?

